==Demographics==

The largest ethnic group in Selma is White (Non-Hispanic) (95.9%). 98.7% of the residents in Selma, OR are U.S. citizens.

In 2022, the median property value in Selma, OR was $253,400, and the homeownership rate was 88.8%.<ref>{{cite web | url=https://datausa.io/profile/geo/selma-or | title=Selma, OR &#124; Data USA }}</ref>

